( grunts )
- HUH?

9
00:02:49,458 --> 00:02:51,250
SORRY, TINA.

10
00:02:51,333 --> 00:02:52,541
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

11
00:02:52,625 --> 00:02:54,125
- YEAH, I'M FINE.

12
00:02:54,208 --> 00:02:57,500
- HEY, WHAT'S WITH THIS
HUGE PACKAGE HERE?

13
00:02:57,583 --> 00:02:58,791
- ( chuckles nervously )

14
00:02:58,875 --> 00:03:01,250
